1.00	The_Pebble_and_the_Penguin_(soundtrack)	The Pebble and the Penguin (soundtrack)	The Pebble and the Penguin: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack is the soundtrack to the Don Bluth animated feature The Pebble and the Penguin. Music by Barry Manilow. Lyrics by Bruce Sussman. Songs Arranged and Produced by Barry Manilow. Soundtrack Produced by Barry Manilow and Marc Hulett. Songs performed by Martin Short, Annie Golden and others. Songs and Score performed by The Irish Film Orchestra. This soundtrack is currently out of print.	
